description: I’m not sure what kind of character ๑ is but it makes a great blushing cheek for these shy or embarrassed Japanese emoticons. It is a cute option for blushing cheeks because it is a swirly spiral. Coupled with a cute pouty mouth like ω brings the cuteness to a whole new level. Kawaii :3 This is like the kind of blushing that happens when someone receives a compliment.
